<div id="page-top">
  <div id="page-top-text">
    <h1 class="header">Welcome to Pantry Packer.</h1>
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <h2>Representing <%= current_user.pantry_name %></h2>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="spacer"></div>

<div class="main-content">
  <h3>Find the Perfect Pantry for You.</h3>
  <h4 class="text-muted">Start donating today.</h4>
  <p>Use our <%= link_to 'View Requests', home_view_requests_path%> page to search for pantries that are looking for what you have to donate. Have a particular pantry in mind? Look them up by name to see which items they currently need, and which items they already have a surplus of. Have items to donate that your go-to pantry isn't currently accepting? Search by item to find pantries that are in need of what you've got to give!</p>

  <br>

  <h3>Represent a Pantry and Start Making Requests.</h3>
  <h4 class="text-muted">Get the word out there and get your shelves filled.</h4>
  <p>Signing up for an account on Pantry Packer unlocks the ability to start making requests for the public to see. Once you create an account, visit the <%= link_to 'Manage Pantry', requests_path%> page to to add requests to your pantry. Need a certain item? Create a request asking food donors to bring a specific type of food. Already have a surplus of a particular item? Create a reqeust discouraging the donation of that item so that donors know that you already have enough.</p>

